const categoryDescriptions = {
  "tab-about": "Hi, I'm Charlie. I'm a freelance creative based on the Isle of Wight, specialising in photography, videography, and design. <br><br> I work as a complete one-stop shop for real estate and property marketing. From property photography and video walkthroughs to floor plans and 3D virtual tours, I provide everything estate agents and developers need to showcase homes across the Island. <br><br> Beyond property, I create visual media for local Isle of Wight businesses and global clients. My commercial work ranges from recruitment films and music videos to custom web design and posters. <br><br> At my core, I'm a visual storyteller. I'm also both a company director and a hands-on creative for the production company Deadman; I've shot award-winning short films and helped produce projects that champion local talent. Whether I'm crafting a narrative film or building a website, I bring a friendly, straightforward approach to every project.",
  "tab-real-estate": "I shoot property photography for luxury homes, estate agency listings, and holiday lets across the Isle of Wight. <br><br> To offer a complete marketing package, I also create 3D virtual tours, detailed floor plans, and video walkthroughs—giving you everything you need to make your listings stand out.",
  "tab-travel": "I capture travel and lifestyle photography showcasing the Isle of Wight and global destinations. <br><br> Using a mix of ground and aerial drone photography, I've partnered with local organisations like Wightlink and the NHS to promote Island tourism and create recruitment campaigns highlighting our coastal lifestyle. <br><br> Further afield, I've worked with global brands like Sunsail and Topdeck to capture lifestyle imagery and travel content around the world.",
  "tab-theatre": "I shoot production stills, rehearsal coverage, and promotional photography for performing arts and stage productions on the Island. <br><br> This includes capturing behind-the-scenes rehearsals and official promotional material for Deadman, the award-winning production company where I also serve as a director.",
  "tab-video-travel": "I provide 4K drone and ground videography for tourism boards, resorts, and commercial campaigns. <br><br> I've shot local tourism and recruitment campaigns for Wightlink and the Isle of Wight NHS Trust, and travelled further afield to capture video content for Sunsail and Topdeck. <br><br> Whether it’s aerial drone footage or ground-level storytelling, I focus on creating videos that naturally capture the feel of a destination.",
  "tab-video-music": "I film music videos and live performances for musicians, bands, and touring artists across the Isle of Wight. <br><br> I work closely with musicians to bring original ideas to life for their songs, coming up with the creative concepts, directing the shoot, and editing the final video entirely myself.",
  "tab-video-shorts": "I shoot and edit short films using Isle of Wight locations to tell visual stories. <br><br> Through my role as a director at the production company Deadman, we've received support from the Mike Howley Trust to help bring local stories to the screen. <br><br> These projects have picked up a few laurels along the way, including a category win at the Montreal Independent Film Festival, alongside finalist spots and official selections at Brighton Rocks and Barnes.",
  "tab-video-theatre": "I film promotional trailers and live performance recordings for theatre companies and dance academies. <br><br> As a director at Deadman, I filmed our nationally touring play, The Freshwater Five, creating proof-of-concept and R&D videos to help market the show and secure Arts Council funding. <br><br> Alongside promotional trailers, I also shoot full live performance recordings, such as end-of-term shows for the Joel Morris Dance Academy.",
  "tab-web-branding": "I design custom websites, posters, and brand identities for Isle of Wight businesses. <br><br> On the digital side, I build and maintain websites, including my own portfolio and the official site for my production company, <a href=\"https://hellodeadman.com\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #fff; text-decoration: underline;\">Deadman</a>.. <br><br> For print and digital marketing, I design ads in all required sizes, often using my own photography. Recent work includes advertising campaigns for local holiday lets and promotional posters for the Abbeyfield Society in Shanklin. <br><br> To keep things simple for my clients, I liaise directly with the publications running the ads to confirm dimensions and handle any necessary design tweaks.",
  "tab-floor-plans": "I draw accurate 2D and 3D floor plans for real estate listings and property developments. <br><br> I provide standard floor plans for everyday property sales and lettings. For more complex projects, I use Rayon to create precise, to-scale drawings that are ideal for renovations, commercial space refits, and interior design planning. <br><br> Whether you need a simple layout for an estate agent or a comprehensive spatial map for a pitch, I can deliver clear, professional assets.",
  "tab-3d-tours": "I create interactive spatial walkthroughs using Matterport and Vieweet for Isle of Wight properties and venues. <br><br> By giving potential buyers and guests a true feel for a property's layout and flow, these tours act as a great filter. They help cut down on time-wasters and ensure that in-person viewings are only booked by genuinely interested people.",
};

